{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249564, "create_time": 1655998098, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "非要被鞭子抽才兴奋是吧", "timestamp": 1655998098}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249570, "create_time": 1655998213, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 也不是这个意思...就像平时摸鱼摸太久了就会有负罪感，如果润了以后日子过的也像以前寒暑假那样荒唐就不太好了吧。。", "timestamp": 1655998213}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249575, "create_time": 1655998340, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "有没有想过，也许人每天本来就应该只工作8小时", "timestamp": 1655998340}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249578, "create_time": 1655998433, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "有没有想过，也许人活着的就是为了像寒暑假一样摸鱼", "timestamp": 1655998433}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249579, "create_time": 1655998446, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 我就是Bob这个意思，有没有想过人真实应该怎么活，而不是被定义的该怎么活", "timestamp": 1655998446}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249581, "create_time": 1655998451, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "过个一年就人熟地也熟了。这边喝酒的人还多些，以及这边工作没你想象的那么闲。比起应对压力，更多的是实现自己的人生追求，工作中也会给你足够的挑战。而且没有那些压力就没必要天天借酒消愁吐苦水，可以和朋友们多玩点新花样了，去看音乐剧，看电影，滑雪，运动，干啥都行。发达国家的文娱设施可比国内强多了", "timestamp": 1655998451}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249584, "create_time": 1655998523, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "养个猫，搞个小花园，玩玩烹饪，也是很好的", "timestamp": 1655998523}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249588, "create_time": 1655998653, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 真的吗？在清华待了这么久也没几个真心朋友唉", "timestamp": 1655998653}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249590, "create_time": 1655998733, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 养宠物确实不错\nsrds，据我所知欧洲基本上都没什么夜生活吧", "timestamp": 1655998733}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249602, "create_time": 1655998959, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 可以去美国", "timestamp": 1655998959}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249624, "create_time": 1655999382, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 但是在8小时之外的时间，潜意识里总有要所谓“过得充实”的这种约束在脑子里，然后如果没有“过得充实”就会很自责。以前觉得这是好事，是什么自律，但现在发现这更像是被卷王思维荼毒的后遗症，所以就很羡慕那些可以毫无负罪感地做“不那么正确的事”的人。。。", "timestamp": 1655999382}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249628, "create_time": 1655999476, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 确实没啥夜生活，但可以去朋友家一块喝酒打游戏啊", "timestamp": 1655999476}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249633, "create_time": 1655999594, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Eve: 对，美国倒是有夜生活，有些地方晚上和国内的街道一样，两边都是烧烤摊和露天餐馆，还有人在路边演奏乐器（不过也有吸了麻的在路上", "timestamp": 1655999594}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249635, "create_time": 1655999662, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 这些活动自己玩也可以。dz在国内找什么关系的朋友喝酒到国外还这样呗", "timestamp": 1655999662}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249640, "create_time": 1655999776, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: cz躺平在床上无所事事的时候也很有负罪感，但出去玩或者做一些活动的体验还挺充实的，就和干了活一样充实", "timestamp": 1655999776}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249650, "create_time": 1655999947, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "去过美国半年，在美国想要留下并且活的不错也不是一件容易的事情，自然环境挺好的，文化饮食上会有不适应。对我而言，是各有各的特点吧，看人的偏好。", "timestamp": 1655999947}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 249694, "create_time": 1656000906, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re 洞主: 找个爱好吧！\n我准备润了之后学画画，年年去那边的漫展摆摊", "timestamp": 1656000906}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 250166, "create_time": 1656033312, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "这😂 看来我有必要把初到美国系列的休闲游玩篇开始写了", "timestamp": 1656033312}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 250192, "create_time": 1656034906, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Hans: 蹲个洞号", "timestamp": 1656034906}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 250245, "create_time": 1656037711, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "润了不就是为了无聊  等我润了天天看书学自己高中想学的", "timestamp": 1656037711}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 250312, "create_time": 1656040795, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "？？美国差不多是全世界最好玩的地方了。而且你有美国护照去哪里玩都方便...", "timestamp": 1656040795}], "create_time": 1655998028, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1656040795, "likenum": 18, "n_attentions": 18, "n_comments": 21, "pid": 71489, "poll": null, "reply": 21, "text": "突然世界观有些晃动。\ndz一直是想润的，理由是想过自由的不卷的属于自己的人生，每天不用背着买房买车带娃的压力还要在大厂做牛做马。但是突然设想了一下真的润了之后的生活，真的会像想象的那样好吗？人生地不熟，想找人下馆子喝酒也没有，有享受生活的消极自由，但是如果没有朋友也很难享受。。以及，没有了买房买车鸡娃的压力好像也随之少了一种对抗人生虚无的方法，有点难。很怕自己再国外那种有大把空余时间的生活方式下逐渐堕落（就像以往的寒暑假一样。。。）\n", "timestamp": 1655998028}}